snippet.title: Devlog 5: Faucet Flood - Freeky Faucets Arcade
snippet.description: Hello peoples I'm actually typing normal to see if this affects anything. This version of Faucet Flood is VERY rough. His design, attacks, arena, even the entrance all eventually get changed. I also mentioned in the video he had another scrapped design. If I can find it I'll post on the community tab and elsewhere. If your interested in the upcoming release of Freeky Faucets follow us on whatever the links are in the bio.
